photon-ltag/
├─ README.md
├─ install.sh
├─ requirements.txt
├─ .env.example
├─ photon/
│  ├─ __init__.py
│  ├─ app.py                 # starts splash → entry → game
│  ├─ db.py                  # Postgres queries (get/add player)
│  ├─ net.py                 # UDP send/receive tasks
│  ├─ scoring.py             # rules & state
│  ├─ audio.py               # mp3 control synced to timer
│  ├─ config.py              # loads env / defaults
│  ├─ ui/
│  │  ├─ splash.py
│  │  ├─ entry.py
│  │  └─ game.py
│  └─ assets/                # logo + base icon + mp3 (from instructor’s GitHub)
│     ├─ logo.jpg
│     ├─ baseicon.jpg
│     └─ tracks/            # mp3s
└─ main.py                   # tiny launcher
